Fig. 4 shows the accuracy loss of FM, FMW, FA and FAW compared with the prediction accuracy of the existing method FE, given the real ratings equal to 2. The accuracy losses of FM, FMW, FA and FAW given the real ratings equal to 2 are higher than the accuracy losses of their corresponding method given the real ratings equal to 1. Similar as the accuracy losses given the real ratings equal to 1, when the real

