relationship between the active user and the recommender. The experimental results show that FA has the best prediction performance among the proposed 4 methods: it can greatly reduce the calculation of rating prediction with only 5%-10% accuracy loss compared with the existing work. The proposed method has great value in the real applications especially when the scale of the network is very large. It greatly reduces the computational complexity with reasonable prediction accuracy.
